ProductGroup.create!(name: 'Concrete Planters', description: 'Our concrete planters come in multiple sizes: 2′, 3′, 4′, 5′, 6′ and 7′. Due to the size and weight of these planters, they provide excellent security barriers while adding to the beauty of commercial properties, parks and recreation areas. Durable construction will hold up well to weather conditions making these planters a practical long-term outdoor showcase for your plants. We offer a variety of colors and finish options to fit your design needs.
If you wish to learn more please feel free to contact our sales support or submit a submission form and we will be happy to assist you in finding the right planter for your project!', image: 'https://www.godawn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Hotchkiss-Showcase-960x420_c.jpg')

ProductGroup.create!(name: 'Fiberglass Planters', description: 'Our fiberglass planters are a care-free solution to beautifying any indoor or outdoor space by adding an attractive home for your plants. These planters are so popular because they are durable, attractive, light, and functional. Available in a wide variety of vibrant colors and finishes to fit whatever your design needs may be. We also offer a wide range of sizes and styles to fit your design needs.

If you wish to learn more please feel free to contact our sales support or submit a submission form and we will be happy to assist you in finding the right planter for your project!', image: 'https://www.godawn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Fiberglass-Planters-Header-Image-768x267.jpg')

ProductGroup.create!(name: 'Plastic Planters', description: 'Our plastic planters are extremely durable, their solid construction will hold up well to harsh weather and long term use without showing signs of wear and tear making them perfect for schools, parks, and unsupervised commercial and residential areas. These plastic planters are an eco-friendly alternative to wood or concrete. Recycled plastic planters are a worry-free long-lasting solution for indoor/outdoor decor and all your planting needs.', image: 'https://www.godawn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Plastic-Planter-Header-Image-768x267.jpg')

ProductGroup.create!(name: 'Metal Planters', description: 'Our metal planters combine design, strength, and durability making them an attractive and long-term solution to your planting needs. We offer many styles, shapes and sizes of metal planters and they are available in many color options to fit your specific design needs.', image: 'https://www.godawn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Metal-Planter-Main-Pic.jpg')

ProductGroup.create!(name: 'Self Watering Planters', description: 'Dawn Enterprises new “Aqueous” self watering planters looks terrific and are the perfect low-maintenance solution for any planting project indoors or outdoors. Save big $$$ on shipping costs without sacrificing that upscale, permanent appearance. This planter ships at a weight of 13 pounds, yet weighs 300 pounds after planting! Create an attractive perimeter to your property without worrying about a huge freight bill; or losing your new planter to inclement weather. Homeowners, property managers, architects, engineers, landscapers, restaurants, convenience stores, retailers, etc. will love the variety of colors offered.', image: 'https://www.godawn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Plastic-Planter-Header-Image-768x267.jpg')

ProductGroup.create!(name: 'Tree Tubs', description: 'Our plastic tree tubs are constructed of medium density linear polyethylene. They have UV inhibitors for outdoor use and prolonged life expectancy. The tanks are nestable which aids in reducing shipping costs. The smooth inner surface makes them easy to clean and their lightweight allows for quick set up and relocation. Our tree tubs are great if you would like to have a small garden but have no room in your yard or you have disagreeable soil. These plastic tree tubs come in a variety of colors to fit your design needs.', image: 'https://www.godawn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Plastic-Planter-Header-Image-768x267.jpg')

ConcretePlanter.create!(product_name: '2ft Cylinder Concrete Planter', price: '$250', description: 'This concrete planter provides a durable and attractive home for your plants. This planter exceeds industrial strength concrete with a minimum rating of 4000 psi at 28 days. Available in a wide variety of colors to fit your design needs.', model: '#PC24x32R', order: '1', image: 'http://www.bigplanters.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/PC24x32R_f.jpg', dimensions: '23.75" dia x 32", 1.5" wall thickness', weight: '435lbs', colors: 'Natural, Charcoal, Brown, Flagstone, Padre Brown, Terra Cotta, White', finishes: 'Natural, Weathered, Light Sand Blast', additional_info: 'For additional information on this product, size options, or to request color samples please call our knowledgable sales team at 1-888-449-0542!', spec: 'https://www.godawn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/PC24x32R.pdf', color_sheet: 'https://www.godawn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/2017-concrete-options.pdf')

ConcretePlanter.create!(product_name: '2ft Square Concrete Planter', price: '$250', description: 'This concrete planter make a spacious home for plants of all sizes! Cast with a drain hole and weep channels, you can rest assured your plants will never be harmed by over watering. These concrete planters are available in a variety of colors and finishes to match any decor.', model: '#PC24x24S', order: '2', image: 'http://www.bigplanters.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/BP-PC24x24x24S_f.jpg', dimensions: '24" cube x 18" tall with 2" tall x 2" deep toe kick at base', weight: '460lbs', colors: 'Natural, Charcoal, Brown, Flagstone, Padre Brown, Terra Cotta, White', finishes: 'Natural, Weathered, Light Sand Blast', additional_info: 'For additional information on this product, size options, or to request color samples please call our knowledgable sales team at 1-888-449-0542!')

ConcretePlanter.create!(product_name: '3ft Round Concrete Deco Base', price: '$300', description: 'Our 3ft round concrete deco base bowl planters make a lovely home for plants of all kinds! Cast with a drain hole and weep channels, you can rest assured your plants will never be harmed by over watering. These concrete planters are available in a variety of colors and finishes to match any decor. Plus, due to their 600 lb weight, they can easily be used as an aesthetically pleasing form of barrier protection.', model: '#PC36RDB', order: '3', image: 'http://www.bigplanters.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/PC36RDB_f.jpg', dimensions: '37.5" Dia. x 20" Height ', weight: '600lbs', colors: 'Natural, Charcoal, Brown, Flagstone, Padre Brown, Terra Cotta, White', finishes: 'Natural, Weathered, Light Sand Blast', additional_info: 'For additional information on this product, size options, or to request color samples please call our knowledgable sales team at 1-888-449-0542!')

FiberglassPlanter.create!(product_name: 'Adamas Fiberglass Tall', price: '$206', description: 'All of our Eco-Fiberglass products have a 30% lower fossil fuel content than normal fiberglass planters. Our Eco-Fiberglass planter line offers aesthetically pleasing planters that are durable and easy to maintain. Available in a wide variety of colors and finishes to suit your design needs.
